    <h2>About Julian Thomas</h2>
 

  <p>Despite having 'always been a photographer' Julian Thomas is self-taught. Until recently he combined photography with another career. Before turning fully professional in September 2000, Julian taught sociology at both universities in Cambridge, UK. He studied with ex-Magnum boss Charlie Harbutt in the summer of 2001 at the Duckspool Photography Centre, Duckspool, UK.</p>

